2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses deep learning techniques to improve classification accuracy. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible sub-category as the paper proposes an automated approach to assess knee OA severity. 
4. cs.MS (Medical Imaging) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with analyzing X-ray images of knee joints. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely sub-category, but still possible as the paper deals with analyzing images.
